00:40:45.750 --> 00:40:46.830
The government is actually
building

00:40:46.830 --> 00:40:47.720
that into their budget.

00:40:47.720 --> 00:40:49.220
And that lets us actually
leverage that local

00:40:49.220 --> 00:40:50.830
government's money.

