If there's financial
malfeasance,

00:42:45.660 --> 00:42:46.390
you got to find it.

00:42:46.390 --> 00:42:48.120
You got to cut it off
at the source.

00:42:48.120 --> 00:42:50.410
And so there's a lot of stuff
