00:43:19.500 --> 00:43:20.700
So I think there's definitely
a role for

00:43:20.700 --> 00:43:22.100
more business people.

00:43:22.100 --> 00:43:24.310
But also, I think we just can't
forget the fact that you

00:43:24.310 --> 00:43:26.020
